# Node
node_modules/

# Trailblaze pack bundle — generated per-pack `.d.ts` files emitted by the
# `trailblaze.bundle` Gradle plugin (and, eventually, `trailblaze bundle` on the CLI).
# Derived from the pack manifest, regenerated on build, not source-of-truth. Anchored
# to the per-pack tools dir so an unrelated future `.trailblaze/` directory elsewhere
# in the tree (e.g., a config dir) isn't silently ignored.
**/trailblaze-config/tools/.trailblaze/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
/sdks/python/.venv/

package-lock.json
bun.lock
bun.lockb